    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Haut: Episode One is an adventure puzzle climbing game that takes you on a breathtaking journey. In this first chapter, the protagonist sets out to find his missing brother, who vanished while searching for hidden treasures. You'll uncover clues to his disappearance as you traverse ancient ruins and towering mountains. Each location holds its mysteries, challenges, and secrets, leading to discoveries that unfold across multiple episodes. Face the harsh elements, encounter unique creatures, and experience the thrill of exploration as the story of Haut begins to unfold. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>EXPLORE</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3110220/extras/39aff771b8bd9e0fc47f68671e73a8fb.poster.avif?t=1768927211\" width=400 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3110220/extras/39aff771b8bd9e0fc47f68671e73a8fb.webm?t=1768927211\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3110220/extras/39aff771b8bd9e0fc47f68671e73a8fb.mp4?t=1768927211\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore the landmarks across the map, solve puzzles to reach your location, and find the hidden treasure!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>SHORT &amp; SWEET</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3110220/extras/695178e870cf56f5198ff6df3c4d7346.avif?t=1768927211\" width=400 height=200 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Complete the story in under an hour while exploring the world!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>ZEN MODE</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3110220/extras/7440162bb31fb84594f8ee263e51ac31.poster.avif?t=1768927211\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3110220/extras/7440162bb31fb84594f8ee263e51ac31.webm?t=1768927211\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3110220/extras/7440162bb31fb84594f8ee263e51ac31.mp4?t=1768927211\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Zen Mode Included to climb without interruption and challenging ledges and obstacles.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Key Features:</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore Different Environments</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Short Game That Can Be Completed In Under Half an Hour</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Zen Mode</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Change Time of Day</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Vibrant &amp; Relaxing Environment</p></li></ul>",
